All programs compile with gcc 4.9 on OSX 10.10 (Yosemite) with the flags found in the makefiles.

To compile, change the CC variable to your C-compiler in any of the makefiles.
All three programs are then compiled by running "make", and ran by running "make run".

All three programs use OpenMP for parallel sections and semaphore.h for synchronization, i.e. for locking, flagging and FIFO mechanisms.